data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in the Deer Run neighborhood, located on a cul-de-sac. The foyer opens into a living room with vaulted ceilings, a fireplace, and wood floors. The kitchen, with stainless steel appliances, leads to a formal dining room. The spacious master suite includes a dual vanity, alongside two additional bedrooms for guests. A finished room over the garage serves as a flexible space for an office, media room, or storage. The back deck overlooks a large backyard, and a detached building provides additional storage or a hobby space. The property features an insulated, powered detached building and an encapsulated crawlspace with a dehumidifier. Located near Historic Downtown New Bern, MCAS Cherry Point, and the Crystal Coast beaches, this home also offers easy access to local shopping and dining. Contact us for more information or to schedule a viewing.
